CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Alta Global Group is a technology company enabling the global martial arts and combat sports industry to maximise the monetization opportunities in the sector by increasing consumer participation in the sport and building upon existing community offerings. Martial arts and combat sports gyms have a superb in-gym product, but they are ripe for transformation in the areas of building sales channels, enhancing customer onboarding, optimizing engagement and driving the growth and retention of members and membership revenues within their communities. Our mission is to unlock the full potential of this sector.
